        3. **SQL Commands**: If database operations are involved
        4. **Other Commands**: API calls, Python commands, etc.
        5. **UI-Only Tasks**: Steps that require pure UI interaction with no command alternative
        
        Return JSON with this structure:
        {{
            "automatable_steps": [
                {{
                    "step_description": "<description of the step>",
                    "linux_commands": ["<cmd1>", "<cmd2>"],
                    "windows_commands": ["<cmd1>", "<cmd2>"],
                    "sql_commands": ["<sql1>", "<sql2>"],
                    "other_commands": ["<other1>", "<other2>"],
                    "automation_level": "<High/Medium/Low>",
                    "notes": "<additional automation notes>"
                }}
            ],
            "ui_only_tasks": [
                {{
                    "step_description": "<description>",
                    "reason": "<why no command automation possible>",
                    "alternative_suggestion": "<possible workaround if any>"
                }}
            ],
            "automation_summary": {{
                "total_steps": <number>,
                "automatable_steps": <number>,
                "ui_only_steps": <number>,
                "automation_percentage": <0-100>,
